\c 97
\s Ukuru hwaJehovha Mambo
\p
\v 1 Jehovha anobata ushe; / nyika ngaifare kwazvo; Zvivi zvizhinji ngazvifare.
\p
\v 2 Makore nerima zvinomukomberedza;
\s Kururama nokururamisa ndidzo nheyo dzechigaro chake choushe.
\p
\v 3 Moto unotungarnira pamberi pake, Uchipisa vadzivisi vake pamativi ose.
\p
\v 4 Mheni dzake dzakavheneka nyika yose;
\s Pasi pakaona, ndokubvunda.
\p
\v 5 Makomo akanyauka senamo pamberi paJehovha,
\s Pamberi paShe wapasi pose.
\p
\v 6 Kudenga-denga kunoparidza kururama kwake,
\s Ndudzi dzose dzakaona kubwinya kwake.
\p
\v 7 Vose, vanoshumira mifananidzo yakaveziwa, vanonyadziswa, Ivo vanozvirumbidza pamusoro
\s pezvifananidzo;
\s Namatai kwaari, imi vamwari vose
\p
\v 8 Zioni rakanzwa ndokufara, Navakunda vaJudha vakafara kwazvo;
\s Nokuda kwezvamakatonga, imi Jehovha.
\p
\v 9 Nokuti imi Jehovha, muri kumusoro-soro kwapasi pose; Makakwirira kupfuura vamwari
\s vose.
\p
\v 10 Vengai zvakaipa, imi munoda Jehovha;
\s Iye anochengeta mweya yavatsvene vake;
\s Unovarwira paruoko rwawakaipa. Chiedza chinodyarirwa wakarurama, Nomufaro vane mwoyo yakarurama.
\p
\v 12 Farai munaJehovha, imi
\s vakarurama;
\s Vongai pakurangarira utsvene hwake.
